data.title: Republic of Moldova: Catalina Grozav, Gr. 16 Tirziu Liliana
data.meta_description:
Republic of Moldova - Free download as Powerpoint Presentation (.ppt / .pptx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or view presentation slides online. (1) The document discusses the Centre of Excellence in Medicine and Pharmacie "Raisa Pacalo" in the Republic of Moldova. 
(2) It introduces the Winery Poiana, located between hills and forests in Ialoveni, and describes its three tour options that include wine tasting and traditional foods.  
(3) It connects the Winery Poiana to the famous Moldovan singer and TV host Adrian Ursu, who was born in the nearby district of Ialoveni.
